name: v1.5.2 - Fix DreamShaper XL Download URL
body:
## Bug Fix

Fixes 404 error when downloading DreamShaper XL model.

### Changed
- Updated DreamShaper XL URL from `Lykon/DreamShaper` to `Lykon/dreamshaper-xl-v2-turbo`
- Affects both individual download and Versatile preset

### How to Update
If you have an existing installation:
```
server-setup > Tools & Monitoring > Update server-setup
```
